tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_execution_latency (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE order_book (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol TEXT,
  buy_sell VARCHAR(5),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  order_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_details (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id INT,
  executed_quantity INT,
  execution_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
CREATE TABLE trade_execution (timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ, trade_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, symbol TEXT, quantity INT, price DECIMAL, execution_latency INTERVAL)
CREATE TABLE trades (trade_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, symbol TEXT, quantity INT, price DECIMAL, execution_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ)
CREATE TABLE order_book (order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, symbol TEXT, order_type TEXT, price DECIMAL, quantity INT, order_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ)
CREATE TABLE trade_logs (log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, trade_id UUID, log_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ, log_message TEXT)
CREATE TABLE latency_metrics (metric_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, trade_id UUID, latency_ms INT, timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ)
